    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, a masterpiece of engineering boasting individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power through a M-Variable Lock differential for optimal lateral traction. The chassis is in showroom state, with zero structural fatigue and a documented rod bearing service. Suspension remains taut, utilizing aluminum control arms and factory-spec bushings to maintain the legendary 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in Alpine White over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its original depth with no signs of oxidation or road rash. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the purist seeking the zenith of the analog driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
