    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the original factory scent still lingers. Every button, screen, and switch operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been exclusively serviced at the original dealership with a comprehensive binder of records included. It drives exactly as it did on delivery day\u2014tight suspension, crisp gear shifts, and a perfectly smooth engine. This is an investment-grade example for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
