      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a definitive example of the E46 chassis. This S54-equipped unit features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip variable M differential. The high-revving 3.2L powerplant has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite, including a dual-VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement with treated shells. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to eliminate floor pan fatigue, a critical structural upgrade for this platform. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution remains communicative. This vehicle is free of fluid seepage and electronic faults, representing a concours-ready specimen for the discerning collector.",
